headline: Is Visa (V) Still Reasonably Priced After Multi Year Share Price Strength?
summary: If you are wondering whether Visa's current share price still offers value, it helps to step back and look at what the recent numbers are actually telling you. Visa shares last closed at US$357.56, with returns of 1.1% over 7 days, 7.9% over 30 days, 3.2% year to date, 15.5% over 1 year, 65.4% over 3 years and 77.5% over 5 years. This gives you a clear snapshot of how the stock has behaved over different time frames. Recent headlines around Visa have largely focused on its role in global...
